Class ArgosMetric

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.im.njams.sdk.argos.ArgosMetric
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JVMMetric
    public abstract class ArgosMetric
extends Object
    Abstract base class for Argos Metrics. Contains the infos about related ArgosComponent

    Extend this class and use it in your @see ArgosCollector Provide all attributes you want to send to Argos.
